  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the different indications to Open Abdomen, the different techniques used to
      perform it, it's management, it's definitive closure and mortality rates linked to the
      different variables. Moreover to evaluate the 1 month and 1 year follow up in patients
      underwent to Open Abdomen.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
